## Limitations

This report is based on available data and publications up to October 2023. The dynamic nature of global conflicts and refugee movements means that new developments may not be captured. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may not reflect the most current statistics or firsthand accounts from refugees themselves. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of the current refugee situation.